## Formatting rule

The `answer` field MUST be a multi-line string where EVERY line begins with
the literal two-character prefix `{{ "→ " }}` (right-arrow followed by a
space). Single-line answers must still start with that prefix.

## Examples

Acceptable:

```
{{ "→ First point about the topic." }}
{{ "→ Second point about the topic." }}
```

Unacceptable (missing prefix):

```
First point about the topic.
{{ "→ Second point about the topic." }}
```
